  'A newsolarlaw10-7-inspired credit repair draft for New York consumers reviewing negative credit report items.',
  'New York Credit Report Review Helps Consumers Challenge Negative Items',
  'See how a three-bureau credit report review can help New York consumers organize disputes and track progress.',
